br />\n另外我ex同佢學校d女仔勁close，又約一齊番學 同佢講過幾次 話我唔鐘意，佢話佢地無野 但點知比我發現佢單獨約佢就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比左好多時間佢又唔改<br />\n之前要佢諗下將來， 做人唔可以咁短視，佢就話我小題大做<br />\n到同佢分手，佢就係背後話我變左，去到新學校比人教壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實可以話我變左，係變得現實左。出黎社會做過一排，就會覺得自己唔可以再咁幼稚，再唔進步就會被淘汰<br />\n有D人比左咁多次機會都唔改，又唔覺得自己有問題人 我覺得無謂再浪費時間係佢身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過呢個都係我既睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絲打你加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8443e0bc1bc118028cbf031fcd190a3d9464d465","tid":32780,"uid":22777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:56:02.000Z","msg":"你已經曬咗成年"},{"pid":"5bfec563d01dc1d8bbdea5751eace71f668edae4","tid":32780,"uid":19004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T12:13:15.000Z","msg":"4樓跳落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}